(1167, 2, '2016-12-14 12:10:58', '2016-12-14 11:10:58', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="entry-content">\r\n\r\nAt last the day has come! Another project is completed. The mobizcorp Berlin branch opened on 1 September, and will have a dual function as a further project development location and customer training centre.\r\n\r\nOur customers will have access to competent contact partners (e-consultants) from the fields of sales, consulting and development, offering our services from modern office premises in a historic building located at the intersection of Chauseestrae and Invalidenstrae, near Friedrichsstrae, in the Berlin-Mitte quarter of the city, the heart of Berlin.\r\n\r\nThe need to open this branch arose from the growing number of customer enquiries, particularly in the software as a service technology area, and we considered Berlin to be the most appropriate location for this.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'mobizcorp Berlin opens', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '405-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-14 12:10:58', '2016-12-14 11:10:58', '', 405, 'http://localhost/preview/405-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
