(1185, 2, '2016-12-14 12:30:47', '2016-12-14 11:30:47', '[vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class="entry-content">\r\n\r\n<em>The action specialist Jochen Schweizer is cooperating with McDonalds in relation to the largest McDonalds Merry MONOPOLY game of all time and is offering take-away prizes and gift vouchers with a total value of more than 40 million euro.</em>\r\n\r\nUntil 3 January 2007, the action specialist Jochen Schweizer will be offering adventures with a value of more than 40 million euro as part of McDonalds Merry MONOPOLY game. All participating McDonalds customers can enjoy the feeling produced by pure adrenalin and win one of the many take-away prizes or gift vouchers.\r\n\r\nJochen Schweizers on-demand eCommerce platform, Demandware, enables the company to effectively and easily manage the more than 4 million voucher codes, which can be cashed in before the end of 2007.\r\n\r\nmobizcorp provided assistance for Jochen Schweizer when the voucher codes were being implemented and managed.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1184" img_size="large"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'BIG MAC and BIG Fun', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1183-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-14 12:30:47', '2016-12-14 11:30:47', '', 1183, 'http://localhost/preview/1183-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
