(1202, 2, '2016-12-14 12:56:12', '2016-12-14 11:56:12', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<em>Under our partnership with etracker, one of the leading web controlling providers on the international market, we are now offering all web controlling services in our portal under attractive terms and conditions.</em>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Increase your online success using real-time web statistics, with analyses of campaigns and live visitor tracking. Save on resources, time and costs thanks to an innovative type of outsourcing forming part of a reasonably priced rental model, without any software installation.\r\n\r\nThanks to etracker you can optimise your online experience and easily improve customer loyalty and your turnover. With etracker you receive all relevant figures in one system, in accordance with laws on data protection, impartially and at low costs.\r\n\r\nWe provide expert advice when you are choosing the tracking strategy that suits your needs and, if requested, would be pleased to integrate it into your website or eCommerce system.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]Follow this link to the <a href="http://mobizcorp.etracker.de" target="_blank">mobizcorp Web Controlling Portal</a>, where you can find all of the information on the topics of tracking and web controlling.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="1201" img_size="large"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'The mobizcorp web controlling portal comes online', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1198-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-14 12:56:12', '2016-12-14 11:56:12', '', 1198, 'http://localhost/preview/1198-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
